{"tid":2496952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推文post:下星期三入境修訂條例草案將會喺立法會恢復二讀，限制香港人出入境自由","createTime":"2021-04-20T07:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:38:37.000Z","uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4962eb72ccef51525177223d0a0a4c2c6aca0791","tid":2496952,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"下星期三（4月28日）入境修訂條例草案將會喺立法會恢復二讀。條例當中列明，入境處長可以被賦予權力，限制任何運輸工具接載或不載個別指定乘客。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會曾經就呢項修訂提出意見書，質疑字眼上相關修訂可以禁止任何人用任何交通工具離開香港，並且無列明入境處長喺咩情況下先可以運用呢個權力。即係話，入境處長可以無限制地運用權力，而呢個權力本身、係會限制香港市民基本嘅出入境自由。<br />\n<br />\n同時公會認為，現時由法院執行嘅法律已經可以限制部分人士離港，並唔需要由入境處長決定，所以好難理解今次修例，係希望達至點樣嘅進一步目的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbPq6Zb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbPq6Zb.jpg&h=eefc9d93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b61823dd28e196f13f60bc523a3dea6be34221f1","tid":2496952,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c030218cf0dae0157a64987c69484be26988201","tid":2496952,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26442459b36c70ab5993c537251a90dec2b8f632","tid":2496952,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"714a0ac53f653ba065125cb27d1fef0d28fa2472","tid":2496952,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"跟住就係學鄰國咁信用系統，評級D連狗巴都冇得上，想返工就用腳行啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c7cf36c35f3279d8bef3c0004cc9e9c1745ed3","tid":2496952,"uid":343610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a79ffcec8a2a05476add6536b885d